urprising trends, examine common misconceptions, and get strategies to better navigate this challenging landscape.</p><dl class=\"detail-list__container\"><div class=\"detail-list__item\"><dt class=\"detail-list__title\"><p>Topics</p></dt><dd class=\"detail-list__desc\"><ul><li>Explore the surprising spread of wildfire, earthquake, and flood risks beyond high-profile regions</li><li>Examine misconceptions about insurance coverage and disaster relief</li><li>Understand shifting underwriting practices and emerging coverage solutions</li><li>Learn how to clearly explain optional coverages, deductibles, and exclusions</li><li>Build stronger client protection with documentation best practices</li></ul></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div style=\"margin:0 auto;max-width:1200px;text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom:15px;\">Choose Your Date and Time</h3><div id=\"webinar-buttons\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;justify-content:center;\"><a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-04-29\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/floods-faults-firestorms-wildfire-earthquake-and-flood-risk-us-20260429\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Wed, April 29 – 11:00 AM EST</a> </div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><section id=\"unlimited\"><hr/></section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A pink piggy bank swims cutely in a bath of gold coins. \" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-